<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV14">
<l>īrvaṉa vēlumañ cēlu muyirmēl miḷirntivaiyō</l>
<l>pērvaṉa vōvalla teyvanal vēḷkaṇaip pēroḷiyē</l>
<l>cōrvaṉa nīlac cuṭarviṭu mēṉiyam māṉvicumpūr</l>
<l>tērvaṉa teyvamaṉ ṉīrakaṇ ṇōvic ceḻuṅkayalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As for these, cutting spears and pretty carps leaping at [my] life,</l>
<l>will they not come back? As the big lights of divine good Desire’s arrows</l>
<l>they will fall. Are they eyes, divine night in essence, that seek the heavenly</l> 
<l>village of the father whose body emits a blue glow, these plump carps?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
